record.title: REMOVAL OF NAME OF MEMBER AS COSPONSOR OF H.R. 1964

speaking.paragraph: Madam Speaker, I ask unanimous consent in the name of Mr. Jon Porter of Nevada that Mr. Porter be removed as a cosponsor of H.R. 1964. Mr. Porter was listed as a cosponsor of H.R. 1964 due to a clerical error.

record.chair: Is there objection to the request of the gentleman from New York?
